name: Test the email Id field does not accept invalid email IDs

testSteps.description: 1: Test the email Id field does not accept invalid email IDs ({email=ca})

children.description: Given user launches Loblaws website
Loblaws Url is opened
When user clicks on sign in link
Then user navigated to Sign in with PC™id page
When user enters "ca" in the EMAIL textbox
Entered the email
Then user gets the validation error message right below the textfield
And a red exclamation mark enclosed in circle is displayed to the right most of the email textfield

testSteps.description: 2: Test the email Id field does not accept invalid email IDs ({email=1})
